      "title": "Prez to make interim-budget speech on August 30",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe as the Minister of Finance will present the Appropriation (Amendment) Bill on August 30, Communications Department of Parliament said.",
        "Accordingly, the President will make the interim-budget speech from 1.00 pm to 2.00 pm on August 30.",
        "The budget debate will be held from 9.30 am to 5.30pm on August 31 and September 1 and 2.",
        "The adjournment debate on the increase in electricity tarrifs will be held on August 29."
      ],
